<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <title>MARKET INTELLIGENCE · SYSTEM INITIALIZING</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      background: #000;
      color: #E0E0E0;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #FF6600;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .sub {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #555;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .box {
      border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
      border-top: 2px solid #FF6600;
      background: #080808;
      padding: 24px 28px;
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .status {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #FFB800;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .msg {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .time {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .bar {
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background: #111;
      margin: 20px 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .bar::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -40%;
      top: 0;
      width: 40%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #FF6600, transparent);
      animation: scan 2s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scan { to { left: 100%; } }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #333;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="logo">▶ MARKET INTELLIGENCE</div>
  <div class="sub">AUTOMATED BRIEFING SYSTEM</div>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="status">⬤ SYSTEM INITIALIZING</div>
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <div class="msg">
      첫 번째 자동 브리핑이 준비 중입니다.<br>
      매일 <strong style="color:#FF6600">오전 7:00 KST</strong>에 자동 업데이트됩니다.<br><br>
      GitHub Actions에서 수동으로<br>
      "Run workflow"를 실행하면<br>
      즉시 브리핑을 생성할 수 있습니다.
    </div>
    <div class="time">NEXT UPDATE: 07:00 KST DAILY</div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    POWERED BY CLAUDE AI · FOR REFERENCE ONLY<br>
    INVESTMENT DECISIONS ARE SOLELY THE RESPONSIBILITY OF THE INVESTOR
  </div>
</body>
</html>
